snippet.title: SOMETHING IN THE WOODS - Teaser
snippet.description:
So many gone missing. Who or... what could have done this. Something's not right. Something's off about those woods. There's something living there. You need to find out what's responsible for this. People need answers. People need you.

Go find for yourself what have done this here: https://differentpixels.itch.io/something-in-the-woods

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DifferentPIxeIs

#gamedev #80s #indiegame #horrorgaming #gamedevelopment
